name Jeret
msg
@match hi|hello
Hi!! How are you? I'm fine!! I LIKE IT
HERE A LOT!!! I know just about anything
about everybody here,except for some
girls in the left wing.Ask me about
anybody!!
@match Toby
He lived pretty much by himself,before
he came here.Toby worked for some
pretty mean people.He had a lot of
friends,and they used to go on
adventures together.He said it was a
lot of fun.Toby likes it here because he
does not have so many problems to deal
with,but he does not like it here
because it's not exciting to him.
@match Jack
Jack is the smallest of us boys here,an'
he gets his way by being cute.His
parents died in the Elven Wars.Jack does
not like to talk about very much,so you
won't get much out of him.
@match Bobby 
 
Bobby does not talk much,so I don't
know much about him.He kind of shy.Nice
though...
@match Tolus
Tolus is an honest to goodness black
elf. Well, at least that is what the
other boys say when he does not agree
with them.Tolus has been sulking
because his friend doesn't live here
anymore.He came here when he was seven
endmsg
